Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.07,0:00:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hear ye, hear ye!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The first post-cutie\Nmark meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Cutie Mark Crusaders\Nis now in session!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I'm sorry Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was distracted by the\Nradiance of my cutie mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's pretty amazing\Nhow the colors just pop off
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,your flank. It's kinda\Nhard to look awa-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. I know our cutie\Nmarks are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But is that all\Nwe're gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just spend our days staring\Ndown at our own flanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I suppose that\Ncould get real boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.92,0:00:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous! We need\Nto go out and do somethin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We need to go try\Nnew stuff like we used to!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Like square dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Or mountain climbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Or square dancing on the\Nmountain we just climbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.24,0:01:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And the more things we try,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the more chances we'll have to\Nfinally get our cutie marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.74,0:01:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.22,0:01:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Apple Bloom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles\Nby YayPonies\NWe have muffins!\Nhttp://yayponies.eu/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow. Did we{\i0}\N{\i1} really only ever do things{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,just to get our\Ncutie marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on. We\Ndid lots of stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that didn't have anything to\Ndo with getting a cutie mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. So, now that we\Ndon't have to do stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to get our cutie marks,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it that the Cutie\NMark Crusaders actually do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We do exactly what we\Ngot our cutie marks in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Helping other ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies without cutie marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Or ponies who've forgotten\Ntheir special purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! We just\Nhave to find ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,who need our help.\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But are you sure\Nyou feel content?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a tinge of\Ndissatisfaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even the slightest\Nnagging sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that you don't really know\Nwhat your purpose is in life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or why you have a big\Napple as a cutie mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The important thing to remember
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is that there is no rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of us tried\Nfor the longest time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.64,0:03:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but it just comes\Nwhen it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's totally\Nnormal to feel confused
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and maybe even\Na little lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But being a blank flank is\Nnothing to be ashamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're having even\Nthe slightest problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Or concerns or questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to know that\Nwe are here to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think they're too\Nworried about it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be a lot\Nharder than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knew there\Nwere so few ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,worried about\Ntheir cutie marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda makes you wonder why\Nwe made such a big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,out of it for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The point is, helping ponies\Nwith cutie mark problems
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.48,0:04:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is what makes us special.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we can't find\Nanypony with a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe we're not special.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I know exactly what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't find a\Ncutie mark problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a cutie mark\Nproblem. It's so confusing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and I feel like\Nthe solution
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is staring me right\Nin the muzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I see why you guys hang\Nout here. It's cozy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crusader Clubhouse is a\Nsafe place, Mr., um... Bulk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A place where we've faced all\Nkinds of cutie mark problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A place where we'll go\Non to solve even more,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,starting with yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how\Nlong it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Or how hard it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll solve it because\Nthat's what we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's your\Ncutie mark problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Right! Uh, well, my\Ncutie mark is a dumb bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've lifted every\Ndumb bell in Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you tried\Nlifting other things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, not\Ndumb bells?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, no. I hadn't\Nthought of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU GUYS ARE AWESOME!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But what happens when I\Nrun out of other stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you could teach\Nother ponies to lift things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!          Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,YEAH! Wow. You three really\Nhave a knack for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That was easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's looking like\Ncutie mark problems
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,are few and\Nfar between.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if we never\Nfind another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if we do, we\Ncould solve it so quick
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be like it never\Nhappened in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.46,0:06:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooo... then the\NCutie Mark Crusaders
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have any\Nreason to exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem\Nboils down to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't need to go out\Nand do things anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.78,0:07:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to get our\Ncutie marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponies with Cutie Mark\Nproblems are hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. But even\Nwhen we find problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we're so good at solving\Nthem that most of the time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing for the\NCutie Mark Crusaders to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I thought we should\Nstart figuring out ways
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to search all of Equestria\Nfor cutie mark problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That kinda seems\Nlike a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think Rarity\Nwould let me travel
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to the far reaches\Nof Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,looking for cutie\Nmark problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm sure we'll come\Nacross them in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we do, we'll\Ntotally solve them
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because we are so\Nawesome at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But what do we\Ndo until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe whatever\Nwe want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we used to only do\Nstuff to get our cutie marks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,or fulfil our destiny,\Nbut now we don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we can do\Nthings just for fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you girls thinking\Nwhat I'm thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Scooting!\NSinging!\NMaking\Npotions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Just remember: Stomp.\NKick. And roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,After this, you two are gonna\Nlove scootering as much as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready? Stomp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,AND ROLL!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Ta-da! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't\Nthink I did it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Doh...mi...soh
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a\Nsimple harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Harmony, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And, ah-one and ah-two\Nand ah-one, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. That was simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a dash and\Na drop and a drip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a dash and a\Ndrop and a drip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though Scootaloo\Nthinks bungee jumping
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is the bees knees,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle would\Nrather keep bees.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm allergic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd have thought\Nit would be so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to find something for\Nus all to do together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I know this might sound\Ncrazy, but what if we didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do things together. Well,\Ndo everything together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're the Cutie\NMark Crusaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And we always will be, but\NI really wanna bungee jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The speed! The height!\NThe fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I know you two\Naren't interested,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:09:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wanna try\Ncrochet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there something
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you've always wanted\Nto do on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I figured we'd\Nalways do stuff together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But bungee jumping\Nsounds just as scary
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,as crochet\Nsounds boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's OK. Sweetie Belle and\NI can do the things we like
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can do\Nwhatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as soon as you\Nfigure out what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Then we\Ncan meet back here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and talk all about\Nwhat we've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know\Nwhat it'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find something!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Something awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I\Nguess now I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I never imagined{\i0}\N{\i1} myself out on my own ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Tryin' to find out{\i0}\N{\i1} what's next for me ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The Cutie Mark Crusaders{\i0}\N{\i1} have always been my home ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Maybe now there's{\i0}\N{\i1} more that I could be ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I guess as{\i0}\N{\i1} time goes by ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Every pony has to{\i0}\N{\i1} go out on their own ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And maybe someday{\i0}\N{\i1} I'll have to try ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Something new{\i0}\N{\i1} that's just for me, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ a little something{\i0}\N{\i1} that could be ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ just my own and I won't{\i0}\N{\i1} feel so left behind ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We used to say that we'd{\i0}\N{\i1} be always side-by-side ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Maybe things are changing{\i0}\N{\i1} and this could mean goodbye ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I always thought{\i0}\N{\i1} our friendship ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Was all I'd ever need ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:12:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ We've always been crusadin'{\i0}\N{\i1} what else is there for me ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I guess as time goes by ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Every pony has to{\i0}\N{\i1} go out on their own ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ And maybe someday{\i0}\N{\i1} I'll have to try ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.68,0:12:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Something new{\i0}\N{\i1} that's just for me ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ A little something{\i0}\N{\i1} that could be ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.88,0:12:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ Just my own and I won't{\i0}\N{\i1} feel so left behind ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And a-one, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Two, two, three, four.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three four.\NTwo, two, three, four--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever kind of\Ndancing y'all are doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you're doing it\Ntogether and I want in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I mean uh,\Nwould it be OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,if I enrolled in\Nthis dance class?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see\Nwhat you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a recital\Nat Town Hall tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and a spot just\Nopened up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tender Taps is a little\Ntoo shy to perform,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you're ready to step\Ninto a partnered routine...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds an awful\Nlot like friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm ready for anything I\Ndon't have to do by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, dancing with\Npartner will be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoaaaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa. Whoaaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew. I feel like that\Nwent pretty good but
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:14:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,let's give it one more whirl\Nbecause it's important
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that I do a good\Njob partnering
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,with my new group\Nof friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehh. Now I'm think of it, you\Nmight be better as soloist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehh, partnering is a\Nlittle advanced for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's still lots\Nyou can do on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but doing\Nstuff on my own
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is exactly what\NI don't want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry it didn't\Nwork out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying different things with\Nmy friends was always fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,even when we were terrible.\NNow it's just terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't that bad; you just\Nneed to learn a few things
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,on your own. Being a\Nsoloist can be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have\Nto do it with feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but\Nwithout my friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll\Never feel again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck at\Nthe recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not going do\Nthat. I mean, I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of all\NI think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet someday my cutie mark\Nwill even be about performing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but I could never dance\Nin front of an audience
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the way I do in class.\NThat's t-t-terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. OK. Nice\Nmeeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle, you are\Nnot going to believe this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think I like\Nbungee jumping
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,even more than scootering!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? That's\Namazing. Look what I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. Uh. That's, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Horrible! But it was so much\Nfun. Rarity showed me how,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,even though she says "crochet\Nis knitting's poorer cousin."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.06,0:16:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Hello, girls. Have fun\Npursuing your own interests?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom? What are you\Ndoing sitting in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We thought\Nyou'd be out looking
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,for things you like to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.66,0:16:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I did. I\Nlooked all over town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked and I\Nlooked and I looked
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know what I found?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried every\None of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And each one just made me feel\Nmore alone than the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see how I'm\Nsupposed to be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're not\Nhanging out anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. I never said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I just said we don't have\Nto do everything together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Like when there's something\None of us wants to do
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that the others don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well, I guess\Nthat changes things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\Nyou thought
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we didn't want to\Nhang out anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you\Ntried all this stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and didn't find one\Nthing you liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I kind of\Nliked dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.98,0:17:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mainly because it\Nlooked like something
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you couldn't do alone, but\NI wasn't very good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be good\Nat something to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And being good doesn't\Nalways mean you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I met the best\Ndancer in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but he was so shy, he couldn't\Nbring himself to perform,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,even though he really,\Nreally wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose this dancing\Npony had a cutie mark, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,SHHHHH!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:18:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me that you wanted to\Nperform more than anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was too caught\Nup in myself to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the best\Ndancer I've ever seen
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm here to convince you\Nto get out on that stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, didn't I also\Ntell you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that dancing in front of other\Nponies is t-t-terrifying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if\Nyou noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...but that auditorium\Nis full of other ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go out there.\NWhat if I'm bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go on together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, you'll look\Ngood dancing next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NI'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have my costume\Nand the backdrop is all wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and we don't have\Ntime to change it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave everything to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You'll\Nbe just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be any\Nworse than I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just what I always\Nimagined it would be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it weren't for all of\Nyou, I wouldn't even have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem. It's\Nwhat we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wish I'd realized\Nwhat you needed right away
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of moping\Naround for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, either way, I\Nhope you keep dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I just might.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is a lot of fun\Nand I'm pretty confident
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I was so silly about\Nus all doing our own things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If we hadn't, I might have\Nnever even tried dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Or find out I\Nneeded help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,With each of us going out and\Ntrying things on our own,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be three times as likely\Nto find ponies to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And trying new stuff\Nmight even make us better
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,at helping them, like how\NI used my bungee jumping
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to change the sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Or my crochet to\Nmake the costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, one thing\Nis for sure:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Cutie Mark Crusaders\Nwill never be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.04,0:21:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be better!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,YEAH!
